His funeral is being held at the Addis Ababa university where his colleagues, students and family have gathered. Government officials and diplomats are also expected to attend, the state-linked Fana Broadcasting Corporate reports. Mesfin had been known as a critical figure of successive governments. A geography professor by training, he wrote more than a dozen books on politics, history and culture. He was also a prolific commentator on newspapers and later on social media. --BBC--